@startuml component_architecture
!theme plain

title UIM Agentry Service - Component Architecture

actor "Mobile DevOps Team" as Team
actor "Mobile User" as User

node "Agentry Service Runtime" {
  component "AgentryServer\n(vibe.d REST API)" as Api
  component "AgentryService\n(Dev/Test/Ops Logic)" as Domain
  database "AgentryStore\n(In-Memory Data)" as Store
}

Team --> Api : app/version/test/runtime management
User --> Api : device sync requests
Api --> Domain : route + validate
Domain --> Store : persist/retrieve entities

note right of Domain
Capabilities:
- develop mobile apps + versions
- test runs for app versions
- runtime deploy + operations dashboard
- backend integration endpoints
end note

@enduml
